Project description

Databricks Connect

Databricks Connect allows you to connect popular IDEs such as Visual Studio Code, PyCharm, IntelliJ IDEA,notebook servers, and other custom applications to Databricks clusters.

Databricks Connect is a client library for the Databricks Runtime. It allows you to write code using Spark APIs andrun them remotely on a Databricks cluster instead of in the local Spark session.

Refer to the official docs at https://docs.databricks.com/en/dev-tools/databricks-connect/
